      "id": "jsds-md-1",
      "type": "MARKDOWN",
      "mode": "jshell",
      "source": "# JavaScript Data Science\n\nThis notebook demonstrates data science with JavaScript using:\n\n- **simple-statistics** — descriptive stats, regression, hypothesis tests\n- **mathjs** — algebra, matrices, complex numbers, units\n- Built-in `venus` helpers for data display\n\n## Setup\n\nInstall required packages in the **Packages → npm** tab:\n1. Click **Packages** tab\n2. Click **npm (JavaScript)**\n3. Click `simple-statistics` pill → Install\n4. Click `mathjs` pill → Install",
